org.apache.lucene.queries.payloads

Class PayloadScoreQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.search.Query
      • org.apache.lucene.search.spans.SpanQuery
        • org.apache.lucene.queries.payloads.PayloadScoreQuery

  • public class PayloadScoreQuery
extends SpanQuery
    A Query class that uses a PayloadFunction to modify the score of a wrapped SpanQuery NOTE: In order to take advantage of this with the default scoring implementation (ClassicSimilarity), you must override ClassicSimilarity.scorePayload(int, int, int, BytesRef), which returns 1 by default.
    See Also:
    Similarity.SimScorer.computePayloadFactor(int, int, int, BytesRef)
